Execute install.sh in SOFTWARE as root to install projectpi software.
Then you should be able to call projectpi software by calling 'projectpi' from any directory.

The program in the DEBUG folder can send commands over network to the projectpi software.
Possible commands are:
	shutd			Shuts raspberry pi down
	killsoft		Kills the Software
	reboot			Reboots raspberry pi
	ledred			Sets eye color to red
	ledgreen
	ledblue
	ledyellow
	ledmagenta
	ledtuerkis
	ledwhite
	ledblank
	[Filename].wav	Plays spezified File -> Software crashes when file not found
